channel.title: Error when running the server
channel.description:
Hello guys,
I kinda made this topic cause I somehow was not getting any replies at my previous one, The topic somehow dies when you're not on the first page... And i couldnt double post or bump or whatever.. so yea..
I just want to be able to play this private server I found at the Downloads page.. Please take a look at the topic I made to be able to understand the whole situation cause you would'nt understand If i typed down everything right here.
Link to previous topic: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,531828.0.html
Take a look at the error at the bottom of the page, please. Any help on this is highly appreciated.
Oh, and if I shouldn't have made this topic/ there's a "better" way of getting help with this, sorry.
